name: TRISTE SIRE
description: In the "IN MY SPIRIT" collection, I continued to work on the way others look at us. Here it is the result of the first part which is called: "IN MY SPIRIT". I added this red clown nose as well as a teardrop in the form of a prism. After doing this tears came to my eyes. Loneliness and sadness are the prizes of the clowns that make us laugh. No longer be fooled by appearances, the truth is so much sadder.
